OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1784380679
OL,3,CSouthern Water fined millions after
OL,4,Cdumping sewage illegally off Kent coast
OL,6,FSouthern Water has been fined more
OL,7,Fthan #7 million after dumping sewage
OL,8,Fillegally off the Kent coast between
OL,9,F2019 and 2021.
OL,11,FThe company, said to have caused harm
OL,12,Ffrom "a pattern of repeated incidents
OL,13,Fover several years", pleaded guilty to
OL,14,F13 offences at Medway Magistrates'
OL,15,FCourt last April over sewage
OL,16,Fdischarges at Margate and Broadstairs
OL,17,Fwastewater pumping stations between
OL,18,F2019 and 2021.
OL,26,@tD@FOUuD@SO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/14
