OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1784380679
OL,3,CSouthern Water fined millions after
OL,4,Cdumping sewage illegally off Kent coast
OL,6,FNine counts related to the incidents
OL,7,Fof untreated sewage dumped off the
OL,8,FKent coast while three counts were
OL,9,Fover failure to notify authorities of
OL,10,Fthe discharges as soon as practicable
OL,11,Fand within 24 hours of a warning which
OL,12,Fis a condition of its environmental
OL,13,Fpermit.
OL,15,FA final conviction was for failing to
OL,16,Fhave a standby pump at Margate's
OL,17,Fstation between July 27 2019 and
OL,18,FOctober 4 2020 in breach of its permit.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1784380679
OL,3,CSouthern Water fined millions after
OL,4,Cdumping sewage illegally off Kent coast
OL,6,FThe sentencing at Canterbury Crown
OL,7,FCourt took place across Thursday and
OL,8,FFriday, with Mr Justice Johnson
OL,9,Fimposing a total fine of #7,127,083.
OL,11,FIt comes after the company was fined
OL,12,F#90 million for nearly 7,000 incidents
OL,13,Facross Hampshire, Kent and Sussex in a
OL,14,Fcase brought by the Environment Agency
OL,15,Fin 2021.
OL,17,FOn Friday, Mr Justice Johnson said
OL,18,Fthere were "overall serious failures",
OL,19,Fadding: "The defendant knew the
OL,20,Fimportance of maintaining resilience
OL,21,Fsystems and equipment at these sites.
OL,26,@zD@LOUzD@eO]{D@IOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1784380679
OL,3,CSouthern Water fined millions after
OL,4,Cdumping sewage illegally off Kent coast
OL,6,F"And it knew what the consequences
OL,7,Fwould be if the system or equipment or
OL,8,Findividual components failed.
OL,10,F"It was well aware of the potential
OL,11,Ffor equipment to fail and for the
OL,12,Fessential need for robust maintenance
OL,13,Fand testing procedures.
OL,15,F"That is because of the dozens of
OL,16,Fprevious occasions on which that had
OL,17,Fhappened."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUwD@AOUyD@JO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1784380679
OL,3,CSouthern Water fined millions after
OL,4,Cdumping sewage illegally off Kent coast
OL,6,FHe told the court: "The harm was not
OL,7,Fconfined to a single event, but arose
OL,8,Ffrom a pattern of repeated incidents
OL,9,Fover several years.
OL,11,F"Taken together, the offending caused
OL,12,Fserious degradation of environmental
OL,13,Fquality, significant interference with
OL,14,Fpublic amenity, potential risk to
OL,15,Fpublic health and damage to the
OL,16,Freputation of an important coastal
OL,17,Fcommunity."
OL,26,@nD@TOUsD@AOUyD@KO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1784380679
OL,3,CSouthern Water fined millions after
OL,4,Cdumping sewage illegally off Kent coast
OL,6,FThe judge said Southern Water is a
OL,7,F"very large" organisation with annual
OL,8,Frevenue over the last three years
OL,9,Fbetween #800 million and #1 billion.
OL,11,FHe said it has 174 previous
OL,12,Fconvictions, convicted every year from
OL,13,F1999 to 2016, and convicted as
OL,14,Frecently as April of this year.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@LO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1784380679
OL,3,CSouthern Water fined millions after
OL,4,Cdumping sewage illegally off Kent coast
OL,6,F"The defendant's record of convictions
OL,7,Fshows a protracted history of non-
OL,8,Fcompliance with its legal obligations,
OL,9,Fand a repeated pattern of inadequate
OL,10,Fstaff training, insufficient
OL,11,Finvestment in the infrastructure and a
OL,12,Ffailure properly to maintain equipment.
OL,14,F"It also shows a failure to respond to
OL,15,Fwarnings from the courts, including
OL,16,Fthe resident judge of this court and
OL,17,Fthe Lord Chief Justice.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1784380679
OL,3,CSouthern Water fined millions after
OL,4,Cdumping sewage illegally off Kent coast
OL,6,F"This record of criminality, to the
OL,7,Fgreat detriment of the environment and
OL,8,Fthe community in Kent, is an
OL,9,Fexceptionally serious aggravating
OL,10,Ffactor," he said.
OL,12,FOn Thursday, the court heard details
OL,13,Fof the offences, including an
OL,14,Fintermittent flow of sewage on July 20
OL,15,F2019 at the Margate site that lasted
OL,16,Ffrom about 2am to just before midnight.
OL,18,FThe Environment Agency was not
OL,19,Fnotified until more than 32 hours
OL,20,Fafter the first discharge.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@HO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1784380679
OL,3,CSouthern Water fined millions after
OL,4,Cdumping sewage illegally off Kent coast
OL,6,FElsewhere, on February 16 2021 at the
OL,7,FBroadstairs wastewater station, the
OL,8,Fcourt heard untreated sewage was
OL,9,Fdumped into the sea because of a
OL,10,Fcomputer control fault.
OL,12,FIt lasted for nearly five hours, and
OL,13,Fauthorities were notified at the end
OL,14,Fof the discharge.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1784380679
OL,3,CSouthern Water fined millions after
OL,4,Cdumping sewage illegally off Kent coast
OL,6,FBut prosecutor Andrew Marshall said
OL,7,Fthe sewage that came out into the sea
OL,8,Fat a shorter distance from the shore
OL,9,Fwas "unscreened" ` which means solid
OL,10,Fwaste remained in the sewage ` and
OL,11,Fthat there was a lot of sewage debris
OL,12,Fwashed up on the coast.
OL,14,FWarnings were put in place on the
OL,15,Fbeach between February 17 and 19 while
OL,16,Fcompany-contracted cleaners swept the
OL,17,Fbeach for waste.
OL,19,FPictures shown in court showed the
OL,20,Fpollution on the beach, and sanitary
OL,21,Fitems in the sea.
OL,26,@qD@EOUqD@PO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G10/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1784380679
OL,3,CSouthern Water fined millions after
OL,4,Cdumping sewage illegally off Kent coast
OL,6,FThe court also heard that sewage
OL,7,Fpollution discharges at Margate and
OL,8,FBroadstairs stations between June 16
OL,9,Fand 17 2021 led to 11 bathing waters
OL,10,Fbeing closed by Thanet council for a
OL,11,Fweek in a "high profile pollution
OL,12,Fincident".
OL,14,FPictures shown to court showed waste
OL,15,Fin the water, closure notices and an
OL,16,Fempty beach with a red flag on display.
OL,26,@sD@KOUtD@IO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G11/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1784380679
OL,3,CSouthern Water fined millions after
OL,4,Cdumping sewage illegally off Kent coast
OL,6,FA Southern Water spokesperson said the
OL,7,Fcompany was "deeply sorry", adding:
OL,8,F"Pollution incidents like these are
OL,9,Funacceptable, and we fully recognise
OL,10,Fthe impact they can have on the
OL,11,Fenvironment and the communities we
OL,12,Fserve.
OL,14,F"These events took place more than 5
OL,15,Fyears ago - since then we've made
OL,16,Fsignificant changes. Under a new
OL,17,Fleadership team, backed by new
OL,18,Fshareholders, we've radically
OL,19,Faddressed our culture, governance and
OL,20,Foperations.
OL,26,@oD@MOUoD@ZO]pD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G12/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38613
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1784380679
OL,3,CSouthern Water fined millions after
OL,4,Cdumping sewage illegally off Kent coast
OL,6,F"The actions we took at Margate and
OL,7,FBroadstairs after an internal review
OL,8,Fof the incidents and its various
OL,9,Fcauses included implementing 24/7
OL,10,Foperational cover, taking steps to
OL,11,Fmake the sites less vulnerable to
OL,12,Fpower outages, additional resilience
OL,13,Ftesting, enhanced monitoring and
OL,14,Fconducting relevant repairs.
OL,16,F"Between 2020-2025, we invested more
OL,17,Fthan #28 million on the wastewater and
OL,18,Fsewer network across Thanet to fund
OL,19,Fthese improvements and more - and our
OL,20,Fperformance in these locations has
OL,21,Fsince improved.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G13/14
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38614
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1784380679
OL,3,CSouthern Water fined millions after
OL,4,Cdumping sewage illegally off Kent coast
OL,6,F"Our responsibility now is to continue
OL,7,Fdelivering the improvements that will
OL,8,Fmake a meaningful difference for our
OL,9,Fcustomers and the environment."
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}  G14/14
